KTS 3.0.x installation
----------------------
1. copy content of /www/ to server
2. set chmod to 0777 for /www/attachment, /www/gallery_data
3. set MySQL connection in /www/.config.php
4. in /www/.htaccess set RewriteBase and ErrorDocument
5. in /www/admin/.htaccess set RewriteBase
6. in /www/admin/.htpasswd replace default account by your own
7. upload sql file to MySQL database

Administration is accessible from /www/admin/ (username: default, password: aaaaaa)

